---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact Us - TopOnlineForm" description="Contact TopOnlineForm team for queries regarding Government Jobs, Admit Cards, and Results. We are here to help.">
  
  <div class="bg-blue-900 text-white text-center py-12 px-4 border-b-4 border-red-600">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-wide uppercase">Contact Top Online Form Team</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-blue-200 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase">Get in touch for Help & Support</p>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 space-y-10">

    <div class="bg-white p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
      {/* üí° PRO TIP: Form ko Sach me Email bhejne layak banane ke liye:
         1. https://web3forms.com/ par jao (Free hai).
         2. Apna email dalo, Access Key milega.
         3. Niche input type="hidden" value="YOUR_ACCESS_KEY" me wo key daal do.
      */}
      <form action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit" method="POST" class="space-y-6">
        
        {/* Web3Forms Access Key (Placeholder) */}
        <input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="YOUR_ACCESS_KEY_HERE" />

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-gray-700 uppercase mb-2">Full Name</label>
            <input type="text" name="name" required placeholder="Enter your name" class="w-full p-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-600 focus:border-transparent outline-none transition-all bg-gray-50" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-gray-700 uppercase mb-2">Email Address</label>
            <input type="email" name="email" required placeholder="name@example.com" class="w-full p-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-600 focus:border-transparent outline-none transition-all bg-gray-50" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-gray-700 uppercase mb-2">Your Message</label>
          <textarea name="message" rows="5" required placeholder="How can we help you today?" class="w-full p-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-600 focus:border-transparent outline-none transition-all bg-gray-50"></textarea>
        </div>

        {/* ‚úÖ FIXED: Button Type changed to submit */}
        <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-lg shadow-md transition-transform transform hover:-translate-y-1 uppercase tracking-wider">
          Submit Message
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span>‚ùì</span> Frequently Asked Questions
      </h3>
      
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100 open:ring-2 open:ring-blue-100">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer list-none p-4 text-gray-800">
            <span>How do I apply for a job listed here?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="text-gray-600 mt-0 px-4 pb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            To apply, simply click on the specific job link from our homepage. Scroll down to the 'Important Links' section in the post, and click on 'Apply Online'. This will redirect you to the official government recruitment portal.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100 open:ring-2 open:ring-blue-100">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer list-none p-4 text-gray-800">
            <span>Is TopOnlineForm a Government Website?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="text-gray-600 mt-0 px-4 pb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            No. TopOnlineForm.com is a private informational website. We are NOT affiliated with the Government of India. We only provide updates based on official notifications.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100 open:ring-2 open:ring-blue-100">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer list-none p-4 text-gray-800">
            <span>When will the exam results be declared?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="text-gray-600 mt-0 px-4 pb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Exam results are declared by the respective conducting authority (like SSC, UPSC). As soon as they are announced, we update the direct link on our Result page. Join our Telegram channel for instant alerts.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-600">
        <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-blue-600 uppercase mb-1">Official Support Email</h4>
        <a href="mailto:help@toponlineform.com" class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 hover:text-blue-700">help@toponlineform.com</a>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Expect response in 24-48 hours</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-orange-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-orange-500">
        <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-orange-600 uppercase mb-1">Business & Ads</h4>
        <a href="mailto:business@toponlineform.com" class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 hover:text-orange-700">business@toponlineform.com</a>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Mon - Sat: 10AM - 6PM</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center text-xs text-gray-400 mt-8 mb-4">
      <p>‚ö†Ô∏è Note: We do not provide jobs directly and never ask for money. Please beware of scams.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>
